*ruby-fcgi-0.8.5 (01 Feb 2005)

  01 Feb 2005; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org>
  +files/ruby-fcgi-sigabrt.patch, +ruby-fcgi-0.8.5.ebuild:
